<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <!-- Required meta tags -->
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

        <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
        <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
            integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        />

        <!-- externall css -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />

        <!-- font -->
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kaushan+Script&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:wght@100&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

        <!-- JQuery -->
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>

        <title>Hello, world!</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <!-- title -->
        <div class="container my-4" id="home">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col d-flex flex-row justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    <h1 class="text-white text-end title">Asvy</h1>
                    <div class="sprt"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-white co-title">Make Your <br />Presentation <br />Clear</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- navigator -->
        <section class="container my-4 position-fixed">
            <div class="row px-3">
                <div class="col-2 navigate">
                    <div class="navi active"><img src="img/ui.png" alt="info" width="15" /></div>
                    <div class="navi"><img src="img/face.png" alt="info" width="15" /></div>
                    <div class="navi"><img src="img/play.png" alt="info" width="15" /></div>
                    <div class="navi"><img src="img/person.png" alt="info" width="15" /></div>
                    <div class="line"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- info section -->
        <section class="container-fluid bg-white info py-4">
            <h1 class="text-start py-3 m-auto info-t">What is This?</h1>
            <p class="text-start text-body info-p m-auto py-3">
                Kami mengembangkan sebuah cara untuk membuat naskah presentasi anda lebih sistematis dan lebih mudah untuk diingat
            </p>
            <p class="text-start text-body info-p m-auto py-3">
                Hanya dengan beberapa klik saja, anda akan mendapatkan naskah presentasi yang berurutan dan mudah dibaca
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- how to section -->
        <section class="container-fluid bg-white how my-4 py-4">
            <h1 class="text-start py-3 m-auto how-t">How to Use?</h1>
            <p class="text-start text-body how-p m-auto py-3">
                Kami mengembangkan sebuah cara untuk membuat naskah presentasi anda lebih sistematis dan lebih mudah untuk diingat
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Quick Start -->
        <section class="container-fluid bg-white start my-4 py-4">
            <form action="/start" method="get">
                <h1 class="text-start py-3 m-auto start-t">Quick Start</h1>
                <h4 class="text-center text-body start-h mx-auto my-2 py-3">Jumlah Slide:</h4>
                <div class="slide mx-auto my-2 py-3 rounded-pill d-flex justify-content-around align-items-center">
                    <div class="triangle"></div>
                    <input class="text-white start-count text-center" type="number" name="count" value="1" min="1" />
                    <div class="triangle"></div>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn d-block mx-auto my-2 py-3 position-relative" style="z-index: 99; width: 30%">
                    <img src="img/start.svg" width="100%" alt="start" />
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <!-- footer -->
        <footer class="container bg-dark py-3">
            <h2 class="text-white text-start foot-t mx-auto p-bottom-3">About Me</h2>
            <p class="text-white text-start foot-p mx-auto py-1 ps-3">
                Aku adalah seorang mahasiswa yang tertarik dengan teknologi, khususnya teknologi web.
            </p>
            <p class="text-white text-start foot-p mx-auto py-1 ps-3">
                Aku sering membuat berbagai projek yang harapannya dapat mempermudah urusan orang lain.
            </p>
            <div class="foot-c text-white text-start mx-auto py-2">
                <p>&copy; Copyright 2021-2022 | by Mukhamad Khusaini. All right reserved</p>
            </div>
        </footer>

        <!-- bootstrap js -->
        <script
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
            crossorigin="anonymous"
        ></script>
        <script src="script.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
